/* magical weapons */
The Master Knight's sword(/d/Kalad/common/caravan/wep/mksword) which
belongs to Artharkan the Master Knight(/d/Kalad/common/caravan/npc/mknight)
is an enchanted weapon that can only be wielded by individuals with a
dis over 100, if someone tries to wield it and fails, they lose a
   randomly determined amount of mana. In addition a minimum sword skill
of 40 (Superior Acolyte) is needed to wield it. This is cumulative
with the >100 dis requirement. Also, the wielder must have an alignment
less than 500. The wielder can also do several emotes.
HIT:41
PEN:41
HANDS:BOTH
UNIQNESS: 4 (only 4 allowed in the game)
-Antharanos-

The Merchant's Bodyguard's axe(/d/Kalad/common/caravan/wep/mbgaxe) which
can be found on the guard(/d/Kalad/common/caravan/npc/mbguard) is an
enchanted weapon that can only be wielded by an individual with a str
over 100, a dis over 100, an axe skill of at least 60 and a spellcraft
skill of at least 20. In addition, no hobbits can wield the weapon due
to its great size. Failure to wield the axe results in a loss of 1000
hp. The axe also has limited healing capabilities. Upon typing the
command word, the axe will heal 500 hp of damage to
its wielder. The axe initially has but 3 charges of healing power,
however, every time someone tries to wield the axe and fails, their
energy is siphoned off and converted into a charge on the axe. The
weapon also has several unique emotes available to its wielder.
HIT:46
PEN:46
HANDS:ONE
UNIQNESS: 4
-Antharanos-

The Skull Knight's warhammer(club)(/d/Kalad/common/caravan/wep/skwarham)
is an enchanted weapon that is wieldable only by individuals with a wis
over 100. If someone tries to wield it and fails, they will lose a
random amount of hit points. A player must also have a strength stat
greater than 50 to wield it.
HIT:41
PEN:43
HANDS:BOTH
-Antharanos-

In the trade district, there is an old human named Penance. He has in 
his possession 2 magic daggers.Penance can be found in 
/d/Kalad/common/trade/cliffside/xzintra.c. The first of his daggers
is a poisoned dagger with 
an increased hit/pen(/d/Kalad/common/trade/cliffside/obj/pdagger).
To wield it, the player must have a con of 80, a dex of 100, and a 
knife skill of 65. Failure to have these stats does no damage, but
increases panic.
HIT:15
PEN:30
HANDS:ANY
Milashk...

The second of Penance's daggers is a parrying dagger. It is enchanted
with an increased hit/pen, as well as additional parry and defence 
skill. To wield it, a player must have a 100 dex, 80 dis, plus a 
75 knife skill. Failure to have these increases panic.
The dagger can be found in /d/Kalad/common/trade/cliffside/obj/p2dagger.c
HIT:30
PEN:25
HANDS:ANY
Milashk...

   The two-handed mithril club (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/wep/gk_club) 
which belongs to the goblin king (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/npc/gob_king)
has the following magical properties. To wield the club, the wielder
must be skilled in its use (50 club skill), cannot be entirely dedicated
to good (alignment < 500) and must not have an intelligence over 100.
Failure to meet any of these requirements when attempting to wield
the club will result in severe fatigue for the person that attempted
the act. The club also has several emotes available.
HIT:44
PEN:44
HANDS:BOTH
-Antharanos-

   The foul stygion-black sword...
(/d/Kalad/common/caravan/wep/sword_of_thanar) belongs to the avatar
of Thanar (/d/Kalad/common/caravan/npc/avatar_thanar) and can only be
wielded by someone with a sword skill of 90, spellcraft of 20 as well
as str,dex,con,int,wis, and dis of at least 100. The weapon has the
special ability, upon utterance of the command word, to grant
temporary invisibility (a little over one minute in RL, or about 20
minutes Kalad time) to its wielder. This ability can only be used 5
times before the weapon becomes powerless.
HIT:50
PEN:50
HANDS:BOTH
UNIQUE: 4
-Antharanos-

   The pure snow-white sword...
(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/wep/sword_of_solara) is a weapon blessed by
Solara, the Kaladian goddess of the sun. To wield it, someone must have
an alignment of at least 1000. The weapon grants upon its wielder the
ability to see into one level of darkness, but only to the wielder, and
only when the weapon is being wielded. The weapon also has the very
limited ability to allow the wielder to see invisible objects (1 level),
but this lasts for little over 1 minute in RL (20 minutes or so Kalad
time). This ability can only be used once before the weapon becomes
powerless.
HIT:45
PEN:45
HANDS:BOTH
-Antharanos-

   The blackened whip...
(/d/Kalad/common/central/wep/lord_whip.c) belongs to the
High Lord of Kabal. It is made of the skin from a black dragon, 
and has a dragon-tooth inside its handle. This weapon is 
'intelligent' in the sence that it has some powers that the 
wielder can use if he/she manages to control the whip. This power 
consists of a special inherit in the weapon. When it hits
a head, and does damage on it, it will add a delay to the
enemy's fighting. (add_attack_delay) for the time: 
20+random(20). The enemy can during this time use their own
specials etch. but they will not use any weapon themselves.
For this special to work, the wielder _must_ set his/her
wimpy to brave.
For each special that is done, the wielder is penaltied 
with max 65 and min 33, depending on spellcraft-skill,
off less mana. If the players mana
reaches 0, the whip will unwield itself and hurt the
wielder with 400 hp. This after a time, so the wielder can
avoid it if fast enough.
   To wield this whip, the player must have Spellcraft of 10,
a club-skill of 60, and a dis of 60. Failure to wield it
means 400hp of damage.
   This whip is un-brawlable when the High Lord wields it.

HIT:48
PEN:40
HANDS:ANY
-Korat-

   The Great War Trident
(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/wep/lmk_trident) belongs to the Lizard Man
King. An artifact from some lost civilization within the desert waste,
it becomes a more effective weapon when wielded by someone of great
strength (STR > 125, hit/pen increases to 48/48). However, it will shock
anyone that attempts to wield it and is insufficiently strong (STR <
126, the weapon will also return to its normal 36/36 hit/pen). The
weapon is coated with the saliva of the Lizard Man King, which acts as
a poison.

HIT:<varies> 48(max)
PEN:<varies> 48(max)
HANDS:BOTH
-Antharanos-

-The Dark Adamantine Sword-(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/wep/h5_1b_sword)
  This sword belongs to the firstboy of House Kilsek in the drow city
of Undraeth (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/npc/h5_firstboy). If a 
person with alignment less than 500 and a sword skill of at least 40
wields it, the sword will radiate 1 level of darkness. If dropped or
unwielded, the sword will cease to radiate darkness.
