-The Great Three-headed Adamantine Flail-(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/wep/h5_p2_flail)
  This flail, found on the Priestess of House Kilsek in the drow city of
Undraeth (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/npc/h5_priest2) will, if 
wielded by a female with a wisdom over 99, have its hit/pen increased
from its normal 20/15 to 40/33. resultantly, when the flail is not
wielded or is wielded by someone that doesn't meet the above 
requirements, it will only have its normal hit/pen. Anyone failing to
wield the flail will be shocked for 500hp of damage.
