-The Large Adamantine Morning Star-(/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/wep/h7_pat_mstar)

   This morning star, found on the patron of House Claddath in the city
of Undraeth (/d/Kalad/common/wild/pass/drow/npc/h7_patron) will, if wielded
by someone with an alignment less than 500 and with a club skill of
at least 50, as well as strength of at least 100, be able to call upon
the morning star's power via a command word. The weapon will do one of
3 things, it will either 1)Heal them physically 2)Heal them mentally or
3) Damage them physically and mentally. If they fail to wield the weapon
then they will lose mana.
