- The blue longsword of Sir Gilbert -
   This is wielded by the deadly avenger of Drakmere, Sir Gilbert. He comes out
with 5 other knights to kill any player who has killed more than 5 citizens or
guards and who has a stat ave of 150 or greater. This sword is only wieldable
by players with alignment of >900, and evil players will be hurt by it with
damage to them equal to their alignment. Players must also have a greater than
100 wisdom. When wielded it adds 8 to your dis. Further, there is a 1/6 change
at each hit that if the enemy is undead, it will do double damage.
