- The  long sharp naginata -

   This is wielded by the beast lord (/d/Kalad/common/raum/npc/blord) who
sits in the dungeons of the temple of the Khiraa. This weapon is special
in that its hit and pen depend on the users skill in polearm. master or
over is 40, veteran and over 30, while the default is 20.
