- Sarr -


- The fire axe -

    This axe is wielded by the High-Lord's most trusted, and personal
guard captain. He guards the High-Lord's wife, in his castle. It is very
hard to get, because in order to kill him, you have to go through 8 of his
guards first, at the same time. Plus, the axe is very deadly, with a hit
and pen of 70/70 when the captain wields it. It has a drawback, tho. It
has a fire special, that goes off randomly. It does about 100 damage a
blow, and takes 100 mana from the wielder. Once the mana runs out, it
stops. So whoever wields this, will have thier mana drained very fast.
HIT: 45
PEN: 48
Hands: both
UNIQUNESS: 4

- Minotaur's Dark-bladed Lochaber Axe -

    This axe is a quest reward, as well as a battle reward. The quest
allows the player to find, and fight the minotaur statue. If the player
defeats it, then the axe is theirs. It is an evil axe, created and
enhanced by an evil warlock. So it can only be wielded by very evil
characters. The quest is a level 3.
